  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is set to detect the impact of bilateral internal iliac artery ligation on the
      amount of intra-operative blood loss during the hysterectomy procedure done for the
      management of abnormally invasive placenta
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
